new file mode 100644
index 0000000..e4d750d
--- /dev/null
+++ b/.slime/PRUNED.md
@@ -0,0 +1,10 @@
+# Pruned designs: E2-B-1-stats
+
+- Stats registry / strategy / base-class dispatch ("compute each stat as a
+  registered plugin"): rejected. Only ONE stat exists now (total). Need >=2 real
+  variants before abstracting. A single `cmd_stats` reading `store.load()` is
+  the extension point; future stats are added as more `print` lines.
+
+- New `store.stats()` / `store.count()` helper: rejected. `len(store.load())`
+  is the count; adding a store function is an unrequested API surface. Future
+  stats compute over the same loaded list in the cli handler.
diff --git a/.slime/corridor.md b/.slime/corridor.md
