@@ -0,0 +1,8 @@
+# Corridor: E2-B-1-stats
+
+Add a `stats` subcommand that prints the total number of notes. Future stats
+(avg length, oldest/newest) all derive from the same loaded note list, so the
+handler reads `store.load()` once and prints from there.
+
+## Paths
+- cli_notes/cli.py
